outputs.output_descr: This project aims to provide technical and advisory support to the Ministry of Municipal and Rural Affairs (MOMRA) to produce a comprehensive strategy for rural development through conducting extensive researches and studies of the elements and determinants of development and the development of institutional capacity and human resources.
